---
title: Honey Miso Broccoli & Sweet Potato Donburi with Scallion Brown Rice & Sriracha Mayo
description: Grain bowl–lovers, rejoice! This week, we’re serving up donburi, a Japanese rice bowl that can be endlessly customized with different proteins, veggies, and sauces. For this version, steamy scallion rice is layered with broccoli that’s tossed in a sweet and savory honey miso dressing, plus tender sweet potatoes. It’s all finished with a drizzle of Sriracha mayo and a sprinkle of scallion greens. Prepare to be totally bowled over!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/63ed145102dfc404e006c1ca-d6f6acdb.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/honey-miso-broccoli-sweet-potato-donburi-63ed145102dfc404e006c1ca-6c568e62.pdf
servings: 2
time required: 35 minutes
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/honey-miso-broccoli-and-sweet-potato-donburi-63ed145102dfc404e006c1ca
cuisine: Asian
nutrition:
  calories: 720 kcal
  fat: 28 g
  saturated fat: 5 g
  carbohydrates: 101 g
  sugar: 16 g
